          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qWQqwVkxpHxcz5jvb_I_-4" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="Browser/Mobile Application" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="40" y="680" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qWQqwVkxpHxcz5jvb_I_-5" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div&gt;Capacity Estimation:&lt;br&gt;For creation flow:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. String (URL): Compress it. 5000 Characters&lt;br&gt;2. Compressing it: 26*26*10&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. 100 URL&#39;s and they create suppose 50 URL&#39;s on avg per day and peak would be 500 URL&#39;s per day.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;100 * 40,000,000,000 -&amp;gt; ~8.6 Million Per day 5000 characters 5KB -&amp;gt; 40GB data per day&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="310" x="490" y="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qWQqwVkxpHxcz5jvb_I_-8" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="User will enter some URL" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="140" x="170" y="670" as="geometry" />
