        <mxCell id="qWQqwVkxpHxcz5jvb_I_-9" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;1. Hashing Mechanism (md5)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Persistent storage somewhere:&amp;nbsp; 1 mapping - long URL to short URL. cluser id: (short url) and partition id: (short url)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Redis - long to short and short to long:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;reading: Cache aside, writing: write through, LFU -&amp;gt; Eliminate extra nodes to sure.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Redis -&amp;gt; Fallback mechanism&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
